Bak move a file to *.bak and use tar to pack the file which you want to backup to a folder like /home/backup.Bak also can recover a file.

How to use
$bak -m file
move file to file.bak
$bak -t file
tar to /home/backup/file-"date".tar.gz
$bak -r file
recover file

=====>2011-7-5<=====
bak-0.1
Simple backup file,like move and tar.
